					<description><![CDATA[In today's edition: FCCPC approves five airtime and data lenders &#124;&#124; M-Tiba to shut down health savings app &#124;&#124; Absa Kenya is spending $23M on digital banking &#124;&#124; Chery's new EV in South Africa]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[



    
    


    <div id="wrapper" style="width:100%;max-width:600px;background-color: #FFFFFF;color:#000000;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin: 0 auto;padding:17px 0">
